#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:1
msgid "DeepSeek-OCR-2"
msgstr "DeepSeek-OCR-2"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:3
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:5
msgid ""
"DeepSeekOCR2 is a model to investigate the role of vision encoders from "
"an LLM-centric viewpoint."
msgstr ""
"DeepSeekOCR2 是一个从以 LLM 为中心的视角研究视觉编码器作用的模型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:7
msgid "The `DeepSeek-OCR-2` model is first supported in `vllm-ascend:v0.16.0`."
msgstr "`DeepSeek-OCR-2` 模型从 `vllm-ascend:v0.16.0` 版本开始首次支持。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:9
msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, "
"including supported features, feature configuration, environment "
"preparation, single-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr ""
"本文档将展示模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点部署、精度评估和性能评估。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:11
msgid "Supported Features"
msgstr "支持的特性"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:13
msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the"
" model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参阅[支持的特性矩阵](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型支持的特性列表。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:15
msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get "
"the feature's configuration."
msgstr ""
"请参阅[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:17
msgid "Environment Preparation"
msgstr "环境准备"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:19
msgid "Model Weight"
msgstr "模型权重"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:21
msgid ""
"`DeepSeek-OCR-2`: [Download model weight](https://huggingface.co"
"/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR-2)."
msgstr "`DeepSeek-OCR-2`：[下载模型权重](https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR-2)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:23
msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of"
" multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录，例如 `/root/.cache/`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:25
msgid "Verify Multi-node Communication(Optional)"
msgstr "验证多节点通信（可选）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:27
msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to verify multi-"
"node communication according to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication)."
msgstr ""
"如果要部署多节点环境，需要按照[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication)验证多节点通信。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:29
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:31
msgid "You can use our official docker image to run `DeepSeek-OCR-2` directly."
msgstr "您可以使用官方 Docker 镜像直接运行 `DeepSeek-OCR-2`。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:33
msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type and start the docker image on "
"your node, refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-"
"docker)."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像，并在节点上启动 Docker 镜像，请参考[使用 Docker 安装](../../installation.md#set-up-using-docker)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/DeepSeekOCR2.md:71
msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to set up "
"environment on each node."
msgstr "如果要部署多节点环境，需要在每个节点上设置环境。"

